snippet.title: Kurdtbada
snippet.description:
Hi, I like to do music mixes, video edits, music samples and make instrumentals with my guitar. I own nothing except this.

All of the music and images posted here are from different artists except my guitar instrumentals, so this is mostly a fan channel dedicated to promote unknown artists from different places.

If you want to remove your music or images from my channel, please contact me in soundcloud.
